  <original-body>Prior to 2.3, OrderedHash#shift returned nil when empty.  In 2.3 it returns [nil, nil].  Hash#shift returns nil in 1.8 and 1.9, so OrderedHash#shift should also.

This bug causes an infinite loop in this idiom:

@@@ ruby
groups = foo.group_by(&amp;:bar)
while group = groups.shift do
  # stuff
end
@@@</original-body>
